724985f-a.title: Queens: 5th Street - 49th Avenue
724985f-a.text:
5th Street, east from near 49th 'Svenue, across the Bong
Island Railroad crossing between 49th and 48th Avenues.
On the left are the Edward Smith Varnish Works and on the
right is the Russell Loft Building (tank thereon). The
building preceding the Loft Building was used by an ice
manufacturing company at one time (1909 map).
P. L. Sperr  November 3, 1930
NO REPRODTCTIONS
